Hey, Gregory and Walter are here,
and they want to say hi.

00:01:55.423 --> 00:01:56.552
&gt;&gt; Dujippi!

00:01:56.552 --> 00:01:58.265
My friend.

00:01:58.265 --> 00:01:59.800
&gt;&gt; Hey.

00:01:59.800 --> 00:02:01.730
&gt;&gt; Hey guys, great to see all of you.

00:02:01.730 --> 00:02:03.430
Actually, I might need to sign off.

00:02:03.430 --> 00:02:06.280
I don't like the way that
parakeet is looking at me.

00:02:07.430 --> 00:02:08.341
&gt;&gt; Okay, bye.

00:02:08.341 --> 00:02:09.014
&gt;&gt; Bye.

00:02:09.014 --> 00:02:09.862
&gt;&gt; Bye.

00:02:09.862 --> 00:02:11.476
&gt;&gt; Have fun.

